•	Target Users: University students and lecturers.
•	Problem: Missed deadlines, scattered assignment information, lack of centralized tracking.
•	Solution: A web-based platform for posting, viewing, and tracking assignments.
•	Key Features:
-	Role-based dashboards (Student, Lecturer)
-	Centralized assignment repository
-	Automated deadline reminders
-	Submission tracking
•	Value Proposition: Reduces missed submissions, improve academic organization, saves time for both students and lecturers.
•	SDG Alignment: Supports SDG4 – Quality Education by promoting equal access to information and better learning outcomes.
•	Competitive Advantage: Education – specific features unlike generic calendar apps.
